            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>We first summarize the characterization of smooth spacelike spherically symmetric constant mean curvature (SS-CMC) hypersurfaces in the Schwarzschild spacetime and Kruskal extension. Then use the characterization to prove special SS-CMC foliation property, and verify part of the conjecture by Malec and Ó Murchadha (Phys Rev D (3) 68:124019, <CitationRef CitationID="CR6">2003</CitationRef>).</Para>
            </Abstract>
